Oravini is a Creator Growth Platform being actively built and shipped.

**Stack:** React (client at `/Users/aryansurana/client/`), Express/Node backend (`/Users/aryansurana/server/`), PostgreSQL with Drizzle ORM (`/Users/aryansurana/shared/schema.ts`), deployed on Render.

**Key features built so far:**
- DM Automation (unified page with Leads, Auto-Replies, Sequences, Send DM, Quick Replies, Instagram tabs)
- Bio Generator Suite
- Video Marketing — fully functional: WebRTC webinars (WebSocket relay, offer/answer/ICE), video hosting with file upload to `/uploads/`, public watch page at `/watch-video/:id` (lead gate, chapters, CTAs, urgency bar), all management APIs (chapters/CTAs CRUD, viewer sessions, view tracking, settings), real analytics replacing fake seeded data
- Content Intelligence, AI Coach, Clip Finder, Video Editor
- Admin + Client layouts with sidebar nav

**Known gotcha:** `client/src/pages/public/` is blocked by global `~/.gitignore` (Public/ rule). New files there need `git add -f` to commit.

**Why:** The user is building and iterating on this product — features get merged directly to main and deployed.

**How to apply:** When making changes, respect the existing component patterns (small focused components, Tailwind + shadcn/ui, dark theme, `text-xs`/`text-sm` sizing). The git repo root is `/Users/aryansurana/` and the working project files are under `client/` and `server/`.
